  fhir:purpose [ fhir:v "To ensure timely follow-up after cervical cancer treatment or triage-negative results, preventing loss to follow-up in the screening cascade. Manages population-specific follow-up intervals and tracks WLHIV double follow-up requirements."] ; # 
